\": 3531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While this video is obviously fake, it is a step towards what counter-disinformation researchers have been warning about - the use of AI manipulated media to enhance foreign disinformation operations,\\\" the State Department said in a statement to CNN.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3669, \"end\": 3671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1627873914309436e-21, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 3781, \"end\": 3784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4444354441466823e-18, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3551}, {\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3583}, {\"ngram\": \"counter-disinformation researchers\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3665}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign disinformation operations\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3734}, {\"ngram\": \"the State Department\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3757}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian Embassy in South Africa shared a version of the video on its X accounts,accordingto screenshots captured by a BBC journalist.\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3791, \"end\": 3806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Westerfeld_House\", \"score\": 0.9999999994847713, \"rank\": 2.0673189282895846e-10, \"text\": \"Russian Embassy\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Westerfeld_House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Weste