pedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a digital forensic expert\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3963}, {\"ngram\": \"professor\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4007}, {\"ngram\": \"hallmarks\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"manipulate\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Farid ran the video through multiple deepfake detection systems and said they indicated that the voices in the video had been created using AI and that the lip movements of the State Department spokesperson in the video had been altered using lip-sync AI software.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4193, \"end\": 4195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1627873914309436e-21, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 4236, \"end\": 4259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Department spokesperson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spokesperson_for_the_United_States_Department_of_State\"}, {\"begin\": 4305, \"end\": 4307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1627873914309436e-21, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Farid\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4072}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple deepfake detection systems\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4116}, {\"ngram\": \"the voices\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4156}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"the lip movements\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4222}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even if the fake is not believed by everyone, the constant bombardment of deepfakes is leading to an overall skepticism of everything we see online,\\\" Farid said.\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fake\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4364}, {\"ngram\": \"the constant bombardment\", \"from\": 4366, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"deepfakes\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4403}, {\"ngram\": \"an overall skepticism\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4439}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4453}, {\"ngram\": \"Farid\", \"from\": 4470, \"to\": 4475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Lee Foster, another information operations expert, expressed skepticism that the imagery in the video was made using AI.\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4487, \"end\": 4490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999999996180122, \"rank\": 3.8044666853181073e-10, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 4491, \"end\": 4497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"score\": 0.9999999948968252, \"rank\": 5.103268896911365e-09, \"text\": \"Foster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\"}, {\"begin\": 4604, \"end\": 4606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1627873914309436e-21, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another information operations expert\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4536}, {\"ngram\": \"skepticism\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4558}, {\"ngram\": \"the imagery\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4575}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at it from an analytic standpoint, it does not make sense to use AI to manipulate mouth movements such that they are basically identical to the original,\\\" Foster told CNN.\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4683, \"end\": 4685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1627873914309436e-21, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 4773, \"end\": 4779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"score\": 0.9999999948968252, \"rank\": 5.103268896911365e-09, \"text\": \"Foster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myles_Birket_Foster\"}, {\"begin\": 4785, \"end\": 4788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4444354441466823e-18, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an analytic standpoint\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4651}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4675}, {\"ngram\": \"mouth movements\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"AI manipulation of the video's audio remains an unresolved question, however.\\\"\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AI